HEADWORD: Discutient
<hw>Dis*cu"tient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>discutiens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>discutere</ets>. See
<er>Discuss</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Serving to disperse
morbid matter; discussive; <as>as, a <ex>discutient</ex>
application</as>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>An agent (as a
medicinal application) which serves to disperse morbid matter.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Foment with <xex>discutiens</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧</def2>
<rj><au>Wiseman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
